@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:3001
@parseId = parse20260412105250938ad9

### 创建 PPT 解析任务（接口 fileType 仍传 "ppt"，但当前 demo 只接受 .pptx 文件）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lesson/parse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolId": "school-demo",
  "userId": "teacher-demo",
  "courseId": "course-ai-001",
  "fileType": "ppt",
  "fileUrl": "file:///E:/CodeWarehouse/A12chaoxin/code/examples/01总论.pptx",
  "isExtractKeyPoint": true,
  "enc": "demo-signature"
}

### 查询解析结果（把 @parseId 替换成上一个请求返回值）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/lesson/parse/{{parseId}}
